"""
    - Test if another worker will pawned if it's already started.
    """
rdb = flask_redislite.FlaskRedis(app, rq=True)
with app.app_context():
    pid = rdb.start_worker()
    assert pid > 0
time.sleep(0.5)
with app.app_context():
    new_pid = rdb.start_worker()
    assert pid == new_pid
rdb.worker_process.terminate()
